パッケージの使用
org.sxb.kit

  • org.sxb.kitを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.sxb.core.scheduling.concurrent
    Scheduling convenience classes for the java.util.concurrent and javax.enterprise.concurrent packages, allowing to set up a ThreadPoolExecutor or ScheduledThreadPoolExecutor as a bean in a Spring context.
    org.sxb.core.scheduling.support
    Generic support classes for scheduling.
    org.sxb.data.redis.listener
    Base package for Redis message listener / pubsub container facility
    org.sxb.ext.kit.jp
    Sxb日语版本支持用工具包
    org.sxb.http
    包含了客户端/服务器端的HTTP基本抽象类 用于Restful
    Contains a basic abstraction over client/server-side HTTP.
    org.sxb.http.converter
    Provides an HttpMessageConverter abstraction to convert between Java objects and HTTP input/output messages.
    org.sxb.kit
    SXB预置工具类包
    已经包含当今非常流行的工具,请尽量优先使用此包中的工具
    org.sxb.plugin.activerecord  
    org.sxb.upload.ext.multipart
    commons fileupload跟Servlet3.0内置上传功能的包装与实现 Multipart resolution framework for handling file uploads.
    org.sxb.upload.ext.multipart.support
    Support classes for the multipart resolution framework.
    org.sxb.web.util
    本包中类尚未启用，后续版本开发预留
